SuchElementException and NullPointerException. The second section's hints seem adequate for the upgrade procedure content. I'm identifying several PascalCase class names scattered throughout the content that should appear in the hints but don't—things like `VariableLengthConvertorSetting`, `SystemRepository`, `DataRecordFormatter`, and `UniversalDao`—which represents a minor V4 gap. Now I'll pull together my final assessment.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":32106,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":32106,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be751b1d-a2a2-4fac-a129-1960c8835fb2","uuid":"7ba6a0e4-45f6-4ff3-ac21-8b532db7f4a6"}
